<author>rạmy hlsh, tạmr qrạʿyn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 fy mḥḍr jlạlk tdẖwb ạlnfs tnḥny
 tḥyṭy brwḥk wʿnd ạlʿrsẖ ạ̉kẖtby
 fạlsạkn fy strk yhym ḥbaⁿạ ynsyn
 yṭyb ạlʿysẖ ʿndk wsẖwq ạlqlb yrtwy
 wḥynmạ tntạbny ẓnwn sẖr wạlqywm
 wtḍʿf ʿzymty wtkẖfy ʿn dẖhny ạlwʿwd
 tjtạj nfsy tḥyyny tʿyd ạlnbḍ llʿrwq
 lstrk trdny tnhy ẓnwny wạlsẖkwk</lyrics>
<title>fy mḥḍr</title>
</song>